Porsche Taycan Viz Pack
======================

Themed custom visualizations for Porsche Taycan EV telemetry
dashboards. Precision instruments on dark glass panels with
ambient glow effects.

Visualizations:
  - battery_gauge:  Segmented ring gauge for battery SOC
  - range_kpi:      Single value tile with sparkline for range
  - charge_gauge:   Horizontal bar gauge for charging power
  - thermal_table:  Temperature sensor table with drilldown
  - energy_area:    Stacked area chart for energy over time
  - regen_donut:    Donut ring for regen vs consumption split

Settings:
  All visualizations support theme (dark/light), accentColor,
  and accentIntensity (0-100) settings via the formatter panel.

  Set panel backgroundColor to "transparent" in Dashboard Studio.

Fonts:
  Outfit (display) and JetBrains Mono (data) are embedded as
  base64 woff2 — no external font requests.
